sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over TrainerV2,S3: Flow 1: Distributed Training Job (MPI/OpenMPI)

        participant TrainerV2 as Kubeflow Trainer v2<br/>Controller
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Rank0 as Training Pod<br/>(rank 0)<br/>SSH:2222/TCP
        participant Workers as Worker Pods<br/>(rank 1..N)<br/>SSH:2222/TCP
        participant GPU as GPU<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>5000/TCP

        TrainerV2->>K8sAPI: Create Pods<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Rank0: Pod Created
        K8sAPI-->>Workers: Pods Created
        Rank0->>Workers: mpirun SSH<br/>2222/TCP<br/>Auth: SSH key pair
        Rank0->>GPU: Compute<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        Workers->>GPU: Compute<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        Note over Rank0,Workers: NCCL/RCCL AllReduce<br/>InfiniBand RDMA<br/>No encryption
        Rank0->>S3: Save checkpoints<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        Rank0->>MLflow: Log metrics<br/>HTTP(S)/5000<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over User,RayDash: Flow 2: Ray Cluster Workload

        participant User as User / Pipeline
        participant RayHead as Ray Head<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>10001/TCP Client
        participant RayWorkers as Ray Workers
        participant RayGPU as GPU<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        participant RayDash as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP

        User->>RayHead: Submit job<br/>Ray Protocol/10001<br/>No encryption
        RayHead->>RayWorkers: Distribute tasks<br/>TCP/6379<br/>No encryption
        RayWorkers->>RayGPU: Compute<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        RayHead->>RayDash: Metrics<br/>HTTP/8265<br/>No encryption
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Browser,S3_WB: Flow 3: Universal Image — Workbench Mode

        participant Browser as User Browser
        participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(Gateway/Route)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Jupyter as Jupyter Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
        participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant S3_WB as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        Browser->>Ingress: Access workbench<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth
        Ingress->>Jupyter: Forward<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>Auth: Platform token
        Jupyter->>HF: Download model<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Jupyter->>S3_WB: Access data<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    end
